# Ps Whole group worked with the code, but we had issues uploading it from different accounts.

When you run the app, you will get 4 options for the 4 features we have.

Option 1: Mood linked habit linking, This option will allow you to pick an emoji based on how you feel and write down your mood.

option 2: Daily Motications: this option will generate a random qoute to cheer you up.

option 3: Challenge mode: This option will allow you to set multiple goals that want to achieve, it works as a checklist in a way.

option 4: Choose today's mode: This option allows you to pick one of 5 emojis and based on which one you choose (your mood) you will get some advice.
